---
<BaseLayout
  title="Accounting Firm Website Design Maryland | Upcoming Brand"
  description="WordPress website design for Maryland accountants and CPA firms. AccountingService schema, client portal integration, 90+ PageSpeed. Fixed-scope from $1,500."
  canonicalUrl="https://upcomingbrand.com/industries/accountant-website-design/"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schemaData)} slot="head" />
  <Navigation />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="lfh-hero">

    <div class="container">
      <nav class="lfh-breadcrumb mono-xs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <a href="/#industries">Industries</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <span>Accountant Website Design</span>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="container lfh-wrap">

      <!-- LEFT COLUMN -->
      <div class="lfh-left">

        <div class="lfh-tags">
          <span class="lfh-pill">
            <span class="lfh-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            CPA &amp; Accounting Web Design &middot; Maryland
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-eyebrow">A specialist studio, not a template shop</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="lfh-h1">
          <span class="lfh-h1-line">Maryland accounting firm websites</span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-accent-line"><em class="lfh-h1-accent">built to attract clients</em></span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-italic">not just look professional.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="lfh-lede">
          Most accounting firm websites don't generate a single new client: no AccountingService schema, no client intake forms, and copy that ranks for nothing. We build WordPress sites for Maryland CPAs and accounting firms that rank for tax and bookkeeping searches, integrate your client portal, and turn visitors into signed engagements. Fixed-scope from <strong>$1,500</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="lfh-ctas">
          <a href="#contact" class="lfh-btn-primary">
            Book a discovery call
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M1 7h12M8 2l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#pricing" class="lfh-btn-ghost">
            See pricing
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M2 12L12 2M12 2H5M12 2v7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="lfh-trust">
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="5.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-opacity="0.35"/><path d="M3.5 6l2 2 3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Maryland-based studio
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">AccountingService schema on every build</span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">Fixed-scope &middot; no surprises</span>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT COLUMN / FORM -->
      <div class="lfh-right">
        <div class="lfh-form-card">
          <div class="lfh-form-header">
            <p class="lfh-form-eyebrow">Free site audit</p>
            <h2 class="lfh-form-title">Is your website generating new clients?</h2>
            <p class="lfh-form-sub">We review your current site and send a plain-English audit within 2 business days. No sales call required.</p>
          </div>

          <form class="lfh-form" name="accountant-inquiry"-honeypot="bot-field" data-uc-form="accountant-inquiry" method="POST" novalidate>
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="accountant-inquiry" />
            <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;" aria-hidden="true">
              <label>Leave blank: <input type="text" name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" /></label>
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="acc-name">Your name</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="text" id="acc-name" name="name" placeholder="David Harrington, CPA" required autocomplete="name" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="acc-email">Email address</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="email" id="acc-email" name="email" placeholder="david@chesapeaketax.com" required autocomplete="email" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="acc-firm">Firm name</label>
